# Sample dataset: raw inputs and tracked labels are tracked so the pipeline can
# be run end-to-end from a fresh clone. Everything derivable from those stays
# out: Cellpose intermediates, the Ultrack working directory, and the contact
# analysis outputs (which also embed absolute paths in their provenance group).
